tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104obc1665703043525.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/obc1665703043525.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/obc1665703043525.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"obc1665703043525\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Component Type\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the type of Uniface Component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"obc1665703043525__section_w1289ab1b5b1_w1290ab1b5_w1291ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Form (FRM) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Interactive component for displaying and\n                        updating data in a desktop environment. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Service (SVC) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Business logic component that can be invoked\n                        locally or remotely. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Report (RPT) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Static component that defines the layout for\n                        presenting data in a printed output. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Entity Service (ESV) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Service that centralizes simple business rules\n                        for single data entities. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">4</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Session Service (SSV) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Service that centralizes complex business\n                        rules affecting multiple data entities. It can be used to manage\n                        task-specific behavior, complex business behavior, transactions, and\n                        referential integrity. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">6</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Static Server Page (USP) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Interactive component for displaying and\n                        updating data. The whole page is updated each time it is refreshed so it is\n                        more suitable to static data. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">7</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__2\"> Dynamic Server Page (DSP) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"obc1665703043525__table_d11054e1_d11055e1_d11056e1__entry__3\"> Interactive component for incrementally and\n                        dynamically displaying and updating data in a web or mobile environment.\n                        Allows only selected data to be updated and supports client-side logic.\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"obc1665703043525__section_j1d_t5r_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d120388e211\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"obc1665703043525__p_d97727e1_d97728e1_d97729e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dhu1704688959391.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dhu1704688959391.html\" title=\"Uniface application components are interchangeable software modules that handle application processing. They are technology-independent, so compiled components can be run on any operating system.\">Components</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"obc1665703043525__section_ztd_jwr_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d120388e227\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"obc1665703043525__ul_dm3_kwr_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"obc1665703043525__li_d39968e1_d39969e1_d39970e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Component Type Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Component Type Specifies the type of Uniface Component. Value Type Description 0 Form (FRM) Interactive component for displaying and updating data in a desktop environment. 1 Service (SVC) Business logic component that can be invoked locally or remotely. 2 Report (RPT) Static component that defines the layout for presenting data in a printed output. 3 Entity Service (ESV) Service that centralizes simple business rules for single data entities. 4 Session Service (SSV) Service that centralizes complex business rules affecting multiple data entities. It can be used to manage task-specific behavior, complex business behavior, transactions, and referential integrity. 6 Static Server Page (USP) Interactive component for displaying and updating data. The whole page is updated each time it is refreshed so it is more suitable to static data. 7 Dynamic Server Page (DSP) Interactive component for incrementally and dynamically displaying and updating data in a web or mobile environment. Allows only selected data to be updated and supports client-side logic. Description For more information, see Components . Applies To Component Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}